News.Title: Visaman Global Sales Plans Warrant Issue
News.Summary: Visaman Global Sales has announced plans to issue up to 4.2 million warrants. Each warrant will be priced at 60 rupees.

News.Title: Visaman Plans Share Issuance of 5.6 Million Shares at 60 Rupees Each
News.Summary: Visaman has announced plans to release up to 5.6 million shares at a price of 60 rupees per share. This share issuance represents a significant corporate action that could impact the company's capital structure and existing shareholders.
